snippet.textDisplay: The music is great, though those drum beats are kind of poky, they can lose those or make them heavier (but not louder). I love the swelling trumpet at the end, I hope that really develops in the film. The suit looks cool. Not keen on the casting though, for other characters as well. Zoe Kravitz is a great choice for Catwoman though, and the Riddler actor seems suitable. Bryan Cranston needs to be Gordon at some point, they should've cast him.
